§ Why ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ Is the sum of two functions integrable? ⦉

  ‖ What is their sum. ⦉
⦉

§ Result ⦉
<statement type='proposition'>
  ‖ Suppose $f, g: 𝗥 → 𝗥$ are integrable. ⦉

  ‖ Then the function $f+g$ is integrable and
    ◇ ⦊
      ‖ ∫f + g = ∫f + ∫g ⦉
    ⦉⦉
</statement>
